WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.160
Now choose the best club for the people below.

00:04.160 --> 00:06.160
One.

00:06.160 --> 00:12.000
Jack plays the guitar really well, but he would like to play with some other people.

00:12.000 --> 00:17.440
He also likes dancing, but has no one to dance with.

00:17.440 --> 00:19.440
Two.

00:19.440 --> 00:26.760
Annie has just received a new camera for her birthday, but she does not know how to use it,

00:26.760 --> 00:29.280
and would like to learn more.

00:29.840 --> 00:30.840
Three.

00:30.840 --> 00:37.680
Dan usually spends his evening watching films on television and DVDs.

00:37.680 --> 00:43.040
He lives a long way from the city centre, and his parents would like him to make some

00:43.040 --> 00:44.160
new friends.

